  {
    
    "name": "Section 6",
    "tag": "section",
    "class": "gps-608137603816161847 gps gpsil",
    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/berkeleylife/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=608137603715170871&sectionId=608137603816161847)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"gghzkoHyojV_text","label":"gghzkoHyojV_text","default":"<strong>Where To Go From Here</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggwqA6Cy44q_text","label":"ggwqA6Cy44q_text","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Two capsules daily. <strong>Berkeley Life works for 24 hours</strong>, the plant-based formula works continuously for 24 hours, supporting blood flow around the clock—maintaining the vascular health that prevents decline from progressing.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">The investment is $42.49 per month with subscription (about $1.40 per day). You're addressing a biological deficit early, when it's most responsive to natural intervention.&nbsp;</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggNQUd1xCSO_text","label":"ggNQUd1xCSO_text","default":"<strong>What Men Are Saying</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggq3WxWMIcn_text","label":"ggq3WxWMIcn_text","default":"<p><i>I've been using this N.O project since 2022, for me it took awhile for it start kicking in for me because I had some underline issues I had to get in control, one was my weight, high blood pressure, diabetes and mildly sexual performance issues. To this product testimony, I worked on myself dropping 40lbs off my weight, that was the big issue and changing my eating habits. That's when this product kicked into full gear for me , my blood pressure start stabilizing, I had good circulation going through my veins, I dropped my A1C to 6.2 from 7.1 My sexual performance got stronger. This product works if you take care of the underline things, I did not had to do a lot to get here. but have this N.O product alone with the test strips to monitor, helped my out tremendously!!! Thank Berkley's for a great product</i></p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggcLOFavrpo_text","label":"ggcLOFavrpo_text","default":"<p><strong>David K., 56</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_D_QMySBg_text","label":"gg_D_QMySBg_text","default":"<p><i>Since I have been taking Berkeley lights nitric acid foundation I have seen my energy levels increase, I also do a lot of cardio running and cycling and have seen benefits as well. Highly recommend.</i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_bVFv9waw_text","label":"gg_bVFv9waw_text","default":"<p><strong>Mateo S. 44</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggG0BS0k_Cp_text","label":"ggG0BS0k_Cp_text","default":"<p><i>I did the test strip and my NO level was very low. Then I took 2 caps of Nitric Oxide Foundation that came n the sample pack, waited 90 minutes. After 90 minutes I retested and my NO level was on the high end. I did not expect that. Genius way of showing the effectiveness of the supplement. I am very impressed.</i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggF1V3gbwGf_text","label":"ggF1V3gbwGf_text","default":"<p><strong>Peter S. 48</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJ_fwPKbcz_text","label":"ggJ_fwPKbcz_text","default":"<p><i>Since day 1, I noticed a significance right away. I’ve tried many N O supplements by far this ranks 1, for me its purity and quality, but most of all it does what it says, that’s nice 😊 to have a standard 963 much needed in this world 🌎 thank you 🙏</i><br>&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggWVfpqvg9H_text","label":"ggWVfpqvg9H_text","default":"<p><strong>Jovani Q. 40</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9SzSdtOLt_text","label":"gg9SzSdtOLt_text","default":"<p>My doctor kept wanting to put me on antidepressants but I tried this first and thank god I did. Feel like myself again without all the weird side effects</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZwfiFFxMk_text","label":"ggZwfiFFxMk_text","default":"<p><strong>Rebecca S., 51</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg34cF7Ioxz_text","label":"gg34cF7Ioxz_text","default":"<u>Frequently asked questions</u>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqzWBcrXNA_childItem_0","label":"ggqzWBcrXNA_childItem_0","default":"<p>What's the correct dosage and how should I take it?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqzWBcrXNA_childItem_1","label":"ggqzWBcrXNA_childItem_1","default":"<p><strong>How long until I feel confident initiating again?</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqzWBcrXNA_childItem_2","label":"ggqzWBcrXNA_childItem_2","default":"<p><strong>Will this help my relationship?</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqzWBcrXNA_childItem_3","label":"ggqzWBcrXNA_childItem_3","default":"<p>How long until I see results?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvTXmAqSlk_text","label":"ggvTXmAqSlk_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);color:rgb(11,11,11);font-size:16px;\">Take two capsules daily with water, preferably after a meal.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggd9CVWV8Oo_text","label":"ggd9CVWV8Oo_text","default":"<p>Most men feel comfortable initiating by weeks 6-8, once function has proven reliable through several successful encounters. Fear of failure decreases as reliability increases. Confidence isn't forced—it returns naturally as capability returns.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggGzD05QpRq_text","label":"ggGzD05QpRq_text","default":"<p>Restoring function removes a significant barrier. Many relationships strengthen significantly once this issue is addressed. Partners often report relief and renewed connection. Addressing the physical foundation creates space for emotional reconnection.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggufosgqD8__text","label":"ggufosgqD8__text","default":"<p>Results vary, some notice a difference right away, while others see benefits after about a month. Consistency is key, and test strips can validate improvements quickly.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gglxyFhpObR_childItem_0","label":"gglxyFhpObR_childItem_0","default":"<p><strong>Will this address the psychological aspect?</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gglxyFhpObR_childItem_1","label":"gglxyFhpObR_childItem_1","default":"<p><strong>Can I just eat more beets instead of taking a supplement?</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gglxyFhpObR_childItem_2","label":"gglxyFhpObR_childItem_2","default":"<p><strong>How is this different from what my medication does?</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gglxyFhpObR_childItem_3","label":"gglxyFhpObR_childItem_3","default":"<p><strong>What improvements should I expect?</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9d3DIlKM9_text","label":"gg9d3DIlKM9_text","default":"<p>Confidence follows capability. When physical function becomes reliable, the psychological burden typically lifts naturally. You stop avoiding because you stop fearing failure. Successful encounters rebuild confidence incrementally. Most men report feeling \"like myself again\" both physically and emotionally by weeks 10-12.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggiOTE1v3r2_text","label":"ggiOTE1v3r2_text","default":"<p>You'd need to consume 7 ounces of beetroot daily to match the concentrated nitrate dose in Berkeley Life's formula. Most people can't sustain that dietary change consistently. Supplementation ensures you get therapeutic levels daily.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggmFQXT5WBV_text","label":"ggmFQXT5WBV_text","default":"<p>Medications force temporary blood vessel dilation by blocking PDE5 enzymes. Berkeley Life supports your body's natural nitric oxide production, which affects blood flow continuously, not just temporarily. It's the difference between forcing a response and supporting the natural mechanism.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggXqsiHg2xM_text","label":"ggXqsiHg2xM_text","default":"<p>Most men notice improved morning readiness within 2 weeks (sign of better natural blood flow), more sustained energy throughout the day, faster recovery from exercise, and overall sense of vitality. Test strips show objective improvement in nitric oxide levels. You're supporting total cardiovascular health, not just one symptom.</p>"}],
    "blocks": [{"type": "@app"}],
    "locales": {}
